#. Tag: title
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Schedule Editor is used to create, edit, calculate and delete schedules."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik urnikov se uporablja za ustvarjanje, urejanje, izračun in "
"brisanje časovnih planov."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Schedule Editor has three sub-views that show the results of the "
"scheduling."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik razporeda ima tri podpoglede, ki prikazujejo rezultate "
"razporejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Result sub-view shows the values needed for PERT analysis including "
"early start and -finish, late start and -finish along with different types "
"of float."
msgstr ""
"Podpogled rezultatov prikazuje vrednosti, potrebne za analizo PERT, vključno "
"z zgodnjim začetkom in ciljem, poznim začetkom in ciljem, skupaj z "
"različnimi vrstami pomičnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Critical Path sub-view shows the tasks that belong to the critical path."
msgstr "Podpogled Kritična pot prikazuje naloge, ki spadajo v kritično pot."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Scheduling Log sub-view shows a list of messages produced during "
"scheduling."
msgstr ""
"Podpogled dnevnika razporejanja prikazuje seznam sporočil, ustvarjenih med "
"razporejanjem."

#. Tag: title
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar provides the means to create, delete and calculate schedules:"
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica ponuja sredstva za ustvarjanje, brisanje in izračun urnikov:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Gumb"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:77 scheduleseditor.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Schedule"
msgstr "Dodaj časovni plan"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Button to create a resource group. The new group is appended at the end of "
"the groups."
msgstr ""
"Gumb za ustvarjanje skupine virov. Nova skupina je dodana na koncu skupin."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Subschedule"
msgstr "Dodaj časovni pod-plan"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Button to create a sub-schedule. The new schedule is appended as a child to "
"the currently selected schedule."
msgstr ""
"Gumb za ustvarjanje časovnega pod-plana. Nov plan je trenutno izbranemu "
"urniku dodan kot podrejeni."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Delete</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izbriši</para>"

#. Tag: keycap
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>Delete</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>Izbriši</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected schedule."
msgstr "Izbriše izbrani časovni plan."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calculate"
msgstr "Izračunaj"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calculates the selected schedule."
msgstr "Izračuna izbrani časovni plan."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Baseline"
msgstr "Izhodišče"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Baselines the selected schedule. Prevents the schedule from being re-"
"calculated or deleted."
msgstr ""
"Osnova izbranega časovnega plana. Preprečuje ponoven izračun ali brisanje "
"časovnega plana."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detach"
msgstr "Loči"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make the selected sub-schedule a top schedule"
msgstr "Izbrani pod-plan naredi za vrhnjega"

#. Tag: title
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Data can be edited in-line as described <link linkend=\"using-the-views"
"\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Podatke je mogoče urejati sproti, kot je opisano <link linkend=\"using-the-"
"views\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following columns are displayed as default:"
msgstr "Naslednji stolpci so privzeto prikazani:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Stolpec"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the schedule."
msgstr "Ime časovnega plana."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "State"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "The schedules state. Shows a progress bar during scheduling."
msgstr "Stanje časovnih planov. Med razporejanjem prikazuje vrstico napredka."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Direction"
msgstr "Smer"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scheduling direction."
msgstr "Smer načrtovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the direction is Forward, the project is scheduled starting at the "
"project's earliest start time specified in the main project dialog. If the "
"direction is Backward, the project is scheduled starting at the project's "
"latest finish time specified in the main project dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če je smer Naprej, je projekt načrtovan za začetek ob najzgodnejšem času "
"začetka projekta, določenem v glavnem pogovornem oknu projekta. Če je smer "
"Nazaj, je projekt načrtovan za začetek ob zadnjem končnem času projekta, "
"določenem v glavnem pogovornem oknu projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overbooking"
msgstr "Presežna rezervacija"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Controls resource overbooking when scheduling."
msgstr "Nadzoruje prezasedenost virov pri razporejanju."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If overbooking is allowed, a resource may be booked (on working days) to "
"work more than it is available. This can happen if the resource is allocated "
"to multiple tasks or are booked on other projects."
msgstr ""
"Če je presežna rezervacija dovoljena, se lahko vir rezervira (ob delovnih "
"dnevih), da deluje več, kot je na voljo. To se lahko zgodi, če je vir "
"dodeljen več nalogam ali je rezerviran za druge projekte."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If overbooking is to be avoided, resources will not be booked more than they "
"are available. On resource conflict, tasks will be delayed until the "
"resource is available."
msgstr ""
"Če se želimo izogniti presežni rezervaciji, viri ne bodo rezervirani več, "
"kot so na voljo. V primeru konflikta virov bodo naloge odložene, dokler vir "
"ni na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "Distribucija"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "The distribution to be used during scheduling."
msgstr "Distribucija, ki bo uporabljena med razporejanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the distribution is 'None', the estimate of the task is used as-is during "
"scheduling."
msgstr ""
"Če je porazdelitev »Brez«, se ocena naloge med razporejanjem uporabi takšna, "
"kot je."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the distribution is 'PERT', the estimate (E) used is calculated based on "
"the entered optimistic- (O), pessimistic-(P) and most likely (M) estimate. "
"The formula used for this is:"
msgstr ""
"Če je porazdelitev 'PERT', se uporabljena ocena (E) izračuna na podlagi "
"vnesene optimistične (O), pesimistične (P) in najverjetnejše (M) ocene. Za "
"to se uporablja formula:"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "E = (O + 4 * M + P) / 6."
msgstr "E = (O + 4 * M + P) / 6."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned Start"
msgstr "Načrtovan začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scheduled start time."
msgstr "Načrtovani začetni čas."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned Finish"
msgstr "Načrtovani zaključek"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scheduled finish time."
msgstr "Načrtovani končni čas."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduler"
msgstr "Razporejevalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scheduler used for calculating the project schedule."
msgstr "Razporejevalnik, ki se uporablja za izračun urnika projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default built-in scheduler is the Network Scheduler."
msgstr "Privzeti vgrajeni razporejevalnik je omrežni razporejevalnik."

#. Tag: title
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu, the view can be configured to split/unsplit the tree "
"view or it can be configured using the configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"S kontekstnim menijem lahko pogled konfigurirate tako, da razdeli/razdeli "
"drevesni pogled, ali pa ga konfigurirate s pogovornim oknom za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: para
#: scheduleseditor.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configure dialog enables you to tailor the amount of information the "
"view displays to fit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da količino informacij, ki jih "
"prikaže pogled, prilagodite svojim potrebam."
